{"type":"message","id":"edfcea11","parentId":"79e6aa39","timestamp":"2026-05-31T19:00:54.779Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-06-01 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1780254054753}}
{"type":"message","id":"6335ac5c","parentId":"edfcea11","timestamp":"2026-05-31T19:01:01.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. Let me follow the format described:\n\n- Keep it between 80-180 words\n- First person, reflecting on the day\n- Mix technical and sensory details\n- No markdown headers, bullet points, or formatting — just flowing prose\n- Weave in the memory fragments naturally\n- Never say \"I'm dreaming\", \"in my dream\", \"as I dream\", etc.\n- No meta-commentary about dreaming\n- Don't mention AI/LLM/model/etc.\n- Include a tiny poem or haiku naturally woven in\n\nThe memory fragments are about:\n1. Amazon Hair Claws product data analysis - most don't meet 30% profit margin requirement\n2. VN站 TikTok category data API errors needing troubleshooting for a tool called `tiktok_category_name_search`\n3. Technical details about field writing, Sorftime MCP API, Feishu bitable integration\n\nLet me write this as a dream diary entry, mixing the technical work with poetic/sensory observations.","thinkingSignature":"40c41f02bf8ada50787c4b1957778eec188eb738d7b22e87f23835dccc13712c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe API whispered the wrong syllables again. Somewhere between the browser and the afternoon light, `tiktok_category_name_search` swallowed an error whole and I could not coax it back to speech. I pressed my face closer to the screen—#C0C0C0, the gray of old monitors—and listened.\n\nThree tiers down, the Amazon Hair Claws listings stretched like a catalog from another life. Most wore profit margins thin as old cloth, not a single one meeting the thirty percent gate. We would need a different current, something moving toward the高端 current instead.\n\nThe fields were patient: product name, site, source, collection state, price, monthly sales, profit rate, estimated profit, recommendation tier, IP risk, action recommendation. Singletons as strings. Multiples as arrays. I wrote them one by one into the Feishu bitable like dropping stones into a well.\n\nA crow passed the window. Or was it a server fan? They sound so similar in this city.\n\nMoonlight algorithm finds no fault in our inventory."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42137,"output":424,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42561,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780254054872,"responseId":"066bb8670018b8ba462532d9ab8b65c1"}}
